trans-unit.source: Provides a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline" /> for media content.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona un objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline" /> para el contenido multimedia.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> is a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> object which provides control over media timing in the same way that animation timeline objects control animations.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> es un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> objeto que proporciona control sobre el control de tiempo medio de la misma manera que los objetos de la escala de tiempo de animación controlan las animaciones.

trans-unit.source: For example, a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> has associated <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.BeginTime%2A> properties can be used to specify when media begins and how long it plays.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, un <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> asociado <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> y <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.BeginTime%2A> propiedades pueden utilizarse para especificar cuándo comienza la media y cuánto tiempo reproduce.

trans-unit.source: See [Animation Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/animation-overview.md) for more information on animation timelines.
trans-unit.target: Vea [información general sobre animaciones](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/animation-overview.md) para obtener más información sobre las escalas de tiempo de animación.

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to associate a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> using a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline>.
trans-unit.target: Hay dos formas de asociar un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> a una <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> mediante un <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline>.

trans-unit.source: Inside of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, when a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> is targets a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>, a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> will be created and assigned to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>’s associated player.
trans-unit.target: Dentro de un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, cuando un <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> es destinos un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> se creará y se asigna a la <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>asociado Reproductor.

trans-unit.source: See [How to: Control a MediaElement by Using a Storyboard](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-control-a-mediaelement-by-using-a-storyboard.md) for an example;
trans-unit.target: Vea [Cómo: controlar un Control MediaElement mediante un guión gráfico](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-control-a-mediaelement-by-using-a-storyboard.md) para obtener un ejemplo;

trans-unit.source: By explicitly creating a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> from a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> and assigning it to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
trans-unit.target: Mediante la creación explícita un <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> desde una <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> y asignarlo a un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> is set to `Automatic` (default), the duration of <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> is the natural duration of the media source.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> de la <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> está establecido en `Automatic` (predeterminado), la duración de <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaTimeline> es la duración natural de origen del elemento multimedia.

trans-unit.source: To find the natural duration of the media source programmatically, query the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement.NaturalDuration%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
trans-unit.target: Para buscar la duración natural de un origen multimedia mediante programación, consultar la <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement.NaturalDuration%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
